<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">
Didnt they add in some sort of RP bonus for being in a full group of 8?<P>I dont have a problem with their being bonuses for grouping, but to be forced to group...no thanks.  At the same time, thats not really the argument Im trying to make.  Its not that I don't want to group (about 90% of my RvR is in a group), but I just don't want to be stuck as being strictly a support character.  I want to be able to nuke down some trolls without taking away from my groups overall performance (ie smite clerics).  I don't want to nuke all the time, or I would have been a wizard; at the same time, I dont want to do support all the time or I would have been a cleric.  Trying to keep people mezzed is often a full-time job, now I have to Un-Mez them too?  The basic point there is dont make me give up my body line all together; I dont want have to to go 44 mind just to get something good.<P>--------------------<P><B>Quote 7/2/02 - i3ullseye, Sorcerer Team Lead: Actually no, i am not 'your' representative. this has been stated before. many TLs do not post ANYWHERE except the pendragn boards. Noone has to try to get ANY feedback from the general populace.</B><P><B>**********************</B><P>Palomides / Alat-Seldi<BR>Mezmo - Level 50.1 Sorcerer<BR>Tagalong - Level 43 Enhance Cleric<BR>Siege - Level 33 Armsman<BR>Terrenus - Level 28 Earth Wizard<BR>Miracle - Level 11 Rejuv Cleric<BR>Recurve - Level 10 Scout
