I don't think were ever geared to be a "pet class".  It's why we never originally (or even now) have spells which enhance our pets.  <P>It seems to me that they just wanted pets to be a sort of bodyguard, a minion.  Not a primary weapon.  They built us around CC and Support.  Make debuffs worth casting and bring us up to par with the other realms' CC.  Then I'll feel that we're more where we should be.
